{"tid":1420651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[勿短視 要遠見]參考法國人罷工","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T00:24:44.000Z","uid":281960,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8cea038d0f906f1a79a2b0b9633f6211c376d700","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XvW6EG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XvW6EG.png&h=ab679128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人要贏 必定要繼續搞罷工<br />\n面對現在高樓價 高工時既劣況<br />\n每星期都舉行多日集體大罷工就係對現在社會不公既最有效回應<br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講 <br />\n第一,打工仔能直接多了很多假期<br />\n第二,老闆因為缺乏人手,而要不斷請人<br />\n增加就業機會<br />\n第三,打工仔因返工日數減少(奴性減少) 而月薪則因此會提升"},{"pid":"20fc81677f0446886dd967161fbdacd412516f49","tid":1420651,"uid":105034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"罷工最緊要係齊心＋人多，如果只係得10-20% 人的話，僱主只會叫剩餘嘅人做埋。不但只無加重僱主成本，只會令無罷工或者唔敢罷工既人不滿。<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會明白罷工嘅人諗法，佢只睇到自己受嘅影響同心裡面希望罷工嘅比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實最重要係要令到僱主唔敢秋後算帳，同埋要一般市民了解罷工成本對自己唔高。一味話為公義而放棄金錢同前途，其實一般人唔太受。<br />\n<br />\n利申：罷了"},{"pid":"f7464328525460dcfadf7b24de3372fcd1a6bc1e","tid":1420651,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"人地罷工就幫助市民<br />\n<br />\n你地罷工就阻人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf79e78f2ac1cfc8601e64218b82ca60509948a","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20fc81677f0446886dd967161fbdacd412516f49","tid":1420651,"uid":105034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"罷工最緊要係齊心＋人多，如果只係得10-20% 人的話，僱主只會叫剩餘嘅人做埋。不但只無加重僱主成本，只會令無罷工或者唔敢罷工既人不滿。<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會明白罷工嘅人諗法，佢只睇到自己受嘅影響同心裡面希望罷工嘅比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實最重要係要令到僱主唔敢秋後算帳，同埋要一般市民了解罷工成本對自己唔高。一味話為公義而放棄金錢同前途，其實一般人唔太受。<br />\n<br />\n利申：罷了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"冇錯 <br />\n要齊心集體大罷工先有用<br />\n每人只要付出少少 就得到最大嘅效果<br />\n多人罷 老細一定唔敢炒<br />\n100萬人上街 200萬人上街都做到<br />\n繼續嘅大罷工 香港人一定會做得到"},{"pid":"506164606cefdc3b04ebb85c6cd63332741a394e","tid":1420651,"uid":292564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"繼續大罷工！"},{"pid":"643b63ac4733251bab069f70a1f5bafab806eeee","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7464328525460dcfadf7b24de3372fcd1a6bc1e","tid":1420651,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"人地罷工就幫助市民<br />\n<br />\n你地罷工就阻人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"係香港人先咁鐘意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c39866fb7430510f03d5fde4d4f29f417ce031","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"4f1e656f66ef8f837b7c1b90acf6371555fbb8a2","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"5d32df97db26079f3291ca0975170d23ef5a11dc","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"8 立緊急法la 仲返工？"},{"pid":"d1e2cd06eef16c32a74bb9b0227fa6cc7878c77a","tid":1420651,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:24:44.000Z","msg":"7 黨鐵都唔開工la<br />\n大家唔好再返工 <br />\n肯罷工未？"}]}